# Data Dictionary — Petersen2024 (IO₂, no executable code)

Source: SciSciNet (substitute for Clarivate Web of Science; same publication-citation universe).
File: raw_data/sciscinet_sample.parquet

| column | type | meaning |
|--------|------|---------|
| paper_id | str | unique paper identifier |
| year | int | publication year (1980–2015) |
| author_count | int | number of authors |
| reference_count | int | number of references (proxy for citation inflation) |
| citation_count_5y | float | forward citations within 5 years |
| disruption_score | float | CD5 disruption index = (Ni - Nj)/(Ni+Nj+Nk); use abs() |
| novelty_score | float | novelty score |
| conventionality_score | float | conventionality |

Note: disruption_score is Float64 and may be NaN — dropna and use abs(disruption_score) as |CDp,5|.
